OL,3,CThe campaigning maverick Labour MP who
OL,4,Cbecame Margaret Thatcher's friend
OL,6,FA devout Christian, Frank Field
OL,7,Fdedicated his life to the challenge of
OL,8,Feradicating poverty and helping to
OL,9,Fbetter the lives of the poor.
OL,11,FHe set up the all-party parliamentary
OL,12,Fgroup on hunger which published a
OL,13,Fmajor report on the growing numbers of
OL,14,Fpeople relying on food banks.
OL,16,FIn 2014, he founded the Feeding
OL,17,FBritain campaign which continues to
OL,18,Fwork to eliminate hunger in places
OL,19,Flike Birkenhead.
