OL,6,FIn 2010, Lord Field became David
OL,7,FCameron's poverty tsar. He reported
OL,8,Fback that improving the life chances
OL,9,Fof children under five was key to
OL,10,Freducing inequality later in their
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,FThe politician was vociferous in his .
OL,15,FHe told the Commons how he had talked
OL,16,Fa Birkenhead man out of taking his own
OL,17,Flife, and how another constituent felt
OL,18,F"lucky" that his family was invited to
OL,19,Feat food left over from a funeral.
