OL,6,FAs chair of the powerful pensions
OL,7,Fselect committee, he notably over the
OL,8,Fcollapse of BHS and had the Royal
OL,9,FLiverpool Hospital's original
OL,10,Fcontractor Carillion in his sights
OL,11,Fwhen it went into liquidation.
OL,13,FFrank Field was an environmentalist
OL,14,Ftoo, arguing that direct action was
OL,15,Fneeded to end deforestation.
OL,17,FIn 2007, he co-founded Cool Earth, a
OL,18,Fcharity that works with native
OL,19,Fcommunities to stop rainforest
OL,20,Fdestruction at its ground roots.
